    "title": "皐月賞の後に・賞賛の方向",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――伝説のウマ娘の『ご令嬢』なのに。\r\n中山レース場ではキングヘイローを見に来た\n観客たちから落胆の声がもれていた。",
            "enText": "—But she's a legend's \"little lady\". The \nspectators at Nakayama Racecourse who came to \nsee King Halo were disappointed.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "pathId": 4446416736059133606,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "だがキングヘイローは諦めない。\r\n次の目標……『日本ダービー』こそは\n必ず取ってみせると誓うのだった。",
            "enText": "But King Halo would not give up. She vowed \nthat her next goal, the… \"Japan Derby,\" \nwould be the one she would take.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 140,
                    "pathId": -3440663649471940562
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 141,
                    "pathId": -5799411674780256447
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6980562829039493388,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "夜、学園に戻ったキングヘイロー。\r\n校門にいたのは母のためにも『日本ダービー』\nを勝ちたいと語るスペシャルウィークだった。",
            "enText": "That evening, King Halo found Special Week \nstanding at the school gates, who'd also want \nto win the Derby, for her mom.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 124,
            "coloredText": [
                {
                    "jpText": "スペシャルウィーク",
                    "enText": "Special Week"
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": -712877067955463679
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": 7759035852563915289
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 160,
                    "pathId": 6826297903572996856
                },
                {
