                    "pathId": -8013724891529867714
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7100792444019643644,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……母の応援を背に頑張る友の姿を見て、\r\nキングヘイローも走り込みを開始する。\n私にも譲れない勝利がある、と。",
            "enText": "… Seeing her friend working hard for her \nmother, King Halo doubles down on training. \nShe, too, has a race she can't lose.",
